// Interpreter fix: ops.rs's Gt dispatch had no (Value::Float, Value::Float)
// arm — only (Value::Num, Value::Num) — so any f64 comparison fell through to
// BadOperands ("operator 'Gt' cannot be applied to float and float"). This is
// a reference-side (interpreter) bug only: the JIT was already correct before
// this fix and should show no behavior difference here.
print(3.14 > 2.0)
